## Problem
B069 probe used N=7 live WAVs. Before flipping ambient default off Vosk, need a broader hit-rate / false-accept picture (speakers, noise, custom names, bare vs greating).

## Goal
Expand `fixtures/voice/wake/` (or parallel eval set) + a small offline runner that scores Vosk and Sherpa KWS (when present) on the same cases.

## Scope
- More positive/negative snips; document capture method
- Script or pytest mark producing a summary table (hit, miss, FA)
- Tie into B070 Sherpa backend once available

## Non-goals
- Full production multi-engine product

